:\"1984\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"Airport Completion and Opening\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"The airport was completed in 1984 following U.S. intervention during Operation Urgent Fury. Its opening marked a pivotal moment in Grenada\\u2019s aviation history, transforming the facility into a cornerstone for regional connectivity and economic growth.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"2009\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"Name Change\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"The airport was officially renamed Maurice Bishop International Airport to honor the visionary leadership of Prime Minister Maurice Bishop and his pivotal role in advancing Grenada\\u2019s aviation and economic development.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"2020\\u2013 2025\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"Recent Upgrades\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Under the China Harbor Engineering Company (CHEC) Project, significant modernization efforts were completed in 2025 to improve safety, efficiency, and passenger experience. Key upgrades include:\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Runway resurfacing and installation of a solar-powered lighting system for sustainable night operations.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Expanded apron, upgraded service lanes, and installation of modern loading bridges to accommodate larger aircraft.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Canopy expansion and bypass road resurfacing for improved traffic flow and passenger comfort.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Construction of a state-of-the-art Emergency Operations Center, along with procurement of a new Air Traffic Management System and PAPI lights for enhanced navigation and safety.\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"BRIEF HISTORY OF MBIA\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Our story takes flight. Where our story took flight\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h2,{children:\"Monuments & Memorials\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Maurice Bishop International Airport is home to two significant monuments that honor lives lost during pivotal moments in Grenada\\u2019s history. These landmarks not only pay tribute to those who served but also stand as enduring symbols of the island\\u2019s complex past.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"Memorial to the Cuban Internationalist Martyrs\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"This memorial honors the 24 Cuban workers who tragically lost their lives during the 1983 conflict and Operation Urgent Fury. The Mausoleum stands as a symbol of Grenada\\u2019s enduring respect and gratitude to those who made the ultimate sacrifice.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"American Monument\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Dedicated to the 19 U.S. servicemen who fell during Operation Urgent Fury, this monument reflects the profound impact of the intervention and its role in shaping Grenada\\u2019s modern history.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h3,{children:\"Reflection & Heritage\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Together, these monuments invite reflection and understanding, offering visitors a deeper connection to Grenada\\u2019s cultural heritage.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"Plaques\"}),\" located at each monument provide historical information and commemorate the individuals whose sacrifices are remembered at these sites.\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"GAA\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"MBIA\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Lauriston Airport\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h4,{children:\"At The Airport\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Car Rental\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Customs Information\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Duty-Free Shops\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Executive Lounge\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h4,{children:\"Useful Links\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Board of Directors\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Management Team\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"FAQ\\u2019s\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.li,{children:\"Careers & Opportunities\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.h2,{children:\"Newsletter\"})]})}function c(i={}){let{wrapper:n}=i.components||{};return n?(0,e.jsx)(n,{...i,children:(0,e.jsx)(d,{...i})}):d(i)}return w(C);})();\n;return Component;"